      • findDesiredSection

        Section findDesiredSection​(PreferenceDao preferenceDao,
                           java.util.List<Section> sections)
                    throws SectionDoesNotExistException
        Finds the desired section. Helper method to get a student's preferences.
        Parameters:
        preferenceDao - the PreferenceDao object that we want to complete building
        sections - a List of Section objects that should contain an ID matching a sectionID found in the PreferenceDao object
        Returns:
        Section object that matches the criteria
        Throws:
        SectionDoesNotExistException - thrown if a section with the desired ID is not in list
